01370 /* dissect raw data */
01371 static int
01372 lustre_dissect_element_data(tvbuff_t *tvb _U_, int offset _U_,
01373                             packet_info *pinfo _U_, proto_tree *parent_tree _U_,
01374                             int hf_index _U_, guint32 buf_num)
01375 {
01376   proto_item *item = NULL;
01377 
01378   guint32 data_len;
01379   int old_offset;
01380 
01381   old_offset = offset;
01382 
01383   data_len = LUSTRE_BUFFER_LEN(buf_num);
01384   if (data_len == 0)
01385     return offset;
01386 
01387   proto_tree_add_item(parent_tree, hf_index, tvb, offset, data_len, TRUE);
01388 
01389   offset += data_len;
01390   proto_item_set_len(item, offset-old_offset);
01391   offset = add_extra_padding(tvb, offset, pinfo, parent_tree);
01392 
01393   return offset;
01394 }

01399 {

01401   int val;
01402   proto_item *item = NULL;
01403 
01404   item = proto_tree_add_item(parent_tree, hf_index, tvb, offset, 0, TRUE);
01405   for (i=0; i < max_length; ++i) {
01406     val = tvb_get_guint8(tvb, offset+i);

01412   return offset;

08248 
08249   /* if (parent_tree) {
08250    *   item = proto_tree_add_item(parent_tree, hf_index, tvb, offset, -1, TRUE);
08251    *   tree = proto_item_add_subtree(item, ett_lustre);
08252    * }
08253    */
08254 
08255   string_len = LUSTRE_BUFFER_LEN(buf_num);
08256   if(string_len == 0)
08257     return offset;
08258 
08259   /*    g_print("buf_num:%d (max:%d) BUFLEN_OFF:%#x strlen:%d\n",

08278 /* Process REINT opcode requests */
08279 static int reint_opcode_process(tvbuff_t *tvb _U_, int offset _U_, packet_info *pinfo _U_, proto_tree * tree _U_)
08280 {
08281   guint32 opcode  ;
08282 
08283   opcode = tvb_get_letohl(tvb,offset);
08284 
08285   switch(opcode){
08286     case  REINT_SETATTR:
08287       /* 2.x+ [rec_setattr][capa1][mdt_epoch][eadata][cookie_data][ldlm_request] */
08288       /* old? [rec_setattr][ldlm_request] */
08289       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_mdt_rec_setattr(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
08290                                                    hf_lustre_mdt_rec_setattr);
08291       if (LUSTRE_BUFCOUNT > 2) {
08292         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_capa(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
08293                                           hf_lustre_capa, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+1);
08294         if (LUSTRE_BUFFER_LEN(LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+2) > 0)
08295           offset=lustre_dissect_struct_mdt_ioepoch(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
08296                                                    hf_lustre_mdt_ioepoch);
08297         offset=lustre_dissect_element_data(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
08298                                            hf_lustre_mds_xattr_eadata,
08299                                            LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+3);
08300         if (LUSTRE_BUFFER_LEN(LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+4) > 0)
08301           offset=lustre_dissect_struct_llog_cookie(tvb,offset,pinfo,tree,hf_lustre_llog_cookie);
08302       }
08303       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ldlm_request(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
08304                                                 hf_lustre_ldlm_request);
08305       break;
08306     case REINT_CREATE :
08307       /* [rec_create][filename][tgt..  0 pour l'instant][ldlm_request] */
08308       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_mdt_rec_create(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_mdt_rec_create);
08309       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_capa(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_capa, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+1);
08310       offset=lustre_dissect_element_string(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_reint_name, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+2);
08311       /* REINT_CREATE_SLAVE / SYM / RMT_ACL */
08312       if (LUSTRE_BUFCOUNT > 4) {
08313         /* for CREATE_SYM this is actually name of target - encoded in mdt_rec_create.cr_mode */
08314         offset=lustre_dissect_element_data(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_reint_name, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+3);
08315         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ldlm_request(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
08316                                                   hf_lustre_ldlm_request);
08317       }
08318       break;
08319     case  REINT_LINK:
08320       /*[mdt_rec_link][filename][ldlm_req] */
08321       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_mdt_rec_link(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_mdt_rec_link);
08322       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_capa(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_capa, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+1);
08323       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_capa(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_capa, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+2);
08324       offset=lustre_dissect_element_string(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_reint_old_name, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+3);
08325       if (LUSTRE_BUFFER_LEN(LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+4) > 0)
08326       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ldlm_request(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ldlm_request) ;
08327       break;
08328     case  REINT_UNLINK:
08329       /* reint_unlink_client: [mdt_rec_unlink][capa1][filename][ldlm_req] */
08330       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_mdt_rec_unlink(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_mdt_rec_unlink);
08331       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_capa(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_capa, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+1);
08332       if (LUSTRE_BUFFER_LEN(LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+2) == 112) {
08333         /* TODO : ugly .. but for now we have to do this */
08334         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_obd_quotactl(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_obd_quotactl);
08335 
08336       } else {
08337         offset=lustre_dissect_element_string(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_reint_name, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+2);
08338         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ldlm_request(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ldlm_request) ;
08339       }
08340       break;
08341     case  REINT_RENAME: /*mds_rename_unpack : [mdt_rec_rename][filename source][filename target_name][ldlm_request] */
08342       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_mdt_rec_rename(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_mdt_rec_rename);
08343       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_capa(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_capa, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+1);
08344       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_capa(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_capa, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+2);
08345       offset=lustre_dissect_element_string(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_reint_old_name, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+3);
08346       offset=lustre_dissect_element_string(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_reint_new_name, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+4);
08347       if (LUSTRE_BUFFER_LEN(LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+5) > 0)
08348         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ldlm_request(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ldlm_request) ;
08349       break;
08350     case  REINT_OPEN: /* [rec_create][filename][eadata] */
08351       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_mdt_rec_create(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_mdt_rec_create);
08352       offset=lustre_dissect_element_string(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_reint_name, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+1);
08353       offset=lustre_dissect_element_data(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_mds_xattr_eadata, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+2);
08354       break;
08355     case  REINT_SETXATTR:
08356       /* 2.x+ [rec_setxattr][capa1][name][eadata] */
08357       /* old? [rec_setxattr][ldlm_request] */
08358       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_mdt_rec_setxattr(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_mdt_rec_setxattr);
08359       if (LUSTRE_BUFCOUNT > 2) {
08360         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_capa(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
08361                                           hf_lustre_capa, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+1);
08362         offset=lustre_dissect_element_string(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_mds_xattr_name, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+2);
08363         offset=lustre_dissect_element_data(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_mds_xattr_eadata,
08364                                            LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+3);
08365         if (LUSTRE_BUFFER_LEN(LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+4) > 0)
08366           offset=lustre_dissect_struct_llog_cookie(tvb,offset,pinfo,tree,hf_lustre_llog_cookie);
08367       } else if (LUSTRE_BUFCOUNT == 2)
08368         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ldlm_request(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
08369                                                   hf_lustre_ldlm_request);
08370       break;
08371     default:
08372       break;
08373 
08374   }
08375 
08376   return offset ;
08377 }

08469 static int
08470 lustre_ost_opcode_process(tvbuff_t *tvb _U_, int offset _U_, packet_info *pinfo _U_, proto_tree * tree _U_, guint32 opc _U_, guint32 pb_type)
08471 {
08472   guint32 i ;
08473 
08474   switch (opc){
08475     case OST_REPLY: /* obsolete so nothing */
08476       break;
08477     case OST_GETATTR:
08478       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ost_body(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ost_body) ;
08479       if (pb_type == PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST)
08480           offset=lustre_dissect_struct_capa(tvb,offset,pinfo,tree, hf_lustre_capa, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+1);
08481       break;
08482     case OST_SETATTR:
08483       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ost_body(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ost_body) ;
08484       if (pb_type == PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST)
08485           offset=lustre_dissect_struct_capa(tvb,offset,pinfo,tree, hf_lustre_capa, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+1);
08486       break;
08487     case OST_READ: /* [OST_BODY][obd_ioobj][niobuf_remote] for request, [OST_BODY] for reply */
08488       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ost_body(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ost_body) ;
08489       if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST){
08490         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_obd_ioobj(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,   hf_lustre_obd_ioobj);
08491         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_niobuf_remote(tvb,offset,pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_niobuf_remote);
08492       }
08493       break;
08494     case OST_WRITE:
08495       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ost_body(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
08496                                             hf_lustre_ost_body);
08497       if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST) {
08498         for (i = 0; i < (LUSTRE_BUFFER_LEN(LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+1))/24; i++)
08499           offset=lustre_dissect_struct_obd_ioobj(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_obd_ioobj);
08500         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_niobuf_remote(tvb,offset,pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_obd_ioobj);
08501       }
08502       if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REPLY) { /* niocount *[uint32], but niocount is in request message, so
08503                                           we use the bufcount */
08504         for (i = 0; i < LUSTRE_BUFCOUNT-2; i++) /* -2 because we have already dissect 2 buffers : ptl + ost */
08505           offset=dissect_uint32(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_nio);
08506         offset=add_extra_padding(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
08507       }
08508       break;
08509     case OST_CREATE:
08510       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ost_body(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ost_body) ;
08511       if (pb_type == PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST)
08512           offset=lustre_dissect_struct_capa(tvb,offset,pinfo,tree, hf_lustre_capa, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+1);
08513       break;
08514     case OST_DESTROY:
08515       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ost_body(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ost_body) ;
08516       if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST) {/* [ost_body][ldlm_req][capa] */
08517         if ( LUSTRE_BUFFER_LEN(LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF +1) != 0)
08518           offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ldlm_request(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ldlm_request);
08519         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_capa(tvb,offset,pinfo,tree, hf_lustre_capa, LUSTRE_REPLY_REC_OFF+2);
08520       }
08521       break;
08522     case OST_GET_INFO:
08523       if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST) /* [key] */
08524         offset=lustre_dissect_element_string(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ost_key, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF);
08525       if (pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REPLY)
08526         offset=lustre_dissect_element_string(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ost_val, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF); /* val */
08527       break;
08528     case OST_CONNECT:
08529       if (pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST) /* [targetuuid][clientuuid][lustre_handle][obd_connect_data] */
08530         offset=lustre_dissect_generic_connect(tvb,offset,pinfo,tree);
08531       if (pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REPLY)
08532         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_obd_connect_data(tvb,offset,pinfo,tree,hf_lustre_obd_connect_data);
08533       break;
08534     case OST_DISCONNECT: /* [nothing] */
08535       break;
08536     case OST_PUNCH: /* [ost_body] */
08537       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ost_body(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ost_body) ;
08538       if (pb_type == PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST)
08539           offset=lustre_dissect_struct_capa(tvb,offset,pinfo,tree, hf_lustre_capa, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+1);
08540       break;
08541     case OST_OPEN: /* [nothing] in the code maybee obsolete */
08542       break;
08543     case OST_CLOSE: /* [nothing] in the code maybee obsolete */
08544       break;
08545     case OST_STATFS: /* [obd_statfs] */
08546       if (pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REPLY)
08547           offset=lustre_dissect_struct_obd_statfs(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_obd_statfs) ;
08548       break;
08549     case OST_SYNC:
08550       /*[ost_body] in both case */
08551       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ost_body(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ost_body) ;
08552       if (pb_type == PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST)
08553           offset=lustre_dissect_struct_capa(tvb,offset,pinfo,tree, hf_lustre_capa, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+1);
08554       break;
08555     case OST_SET_INFO:
08556       if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST)
08557       {
08558         offset=lustre_dissect_element_string(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ost_key, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF); /* key  */
08559         offset=lustre_dissect_element_string(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ost_val, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+1); /* val */
08560       }
08561       /* if Key = "evict_by_nid" --> need to be process.. TODO */
08562       break;
08563     case OST_QUOTACHECK:
08564       if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST)

08586 static int
08587 lustre_mds_opcode_process(tvbuff_t *tvb _U_, int offset _U_, packet_info *pinfo _U_, proto_tree * tree _U_, guint32 opc _U_, guint32 pb_type)
08588 {
08589   switch (opc){
08590     case MDS_DISCONNECT:
08591       /*[nothing]*/
08592       break;
08593     case MDS_GET_ROOT:
08594       /*request: [mds body]*/
08595       /*reply:   [mds body][capa] */
08596       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_mdt_body(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_mdt_body) ;

08599       break;
08600     case MDS_SETXATTR:
08601       if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST)
08602         /* [mds body] */
08603         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_mdt_body(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_mdt_body) ;
08604       /*if(reply) : [nothing]*/
08605       break;
08606     case MDS_GETXATTR:
08607       /*request: [mds body][capa][xattr name]*/
08608       /*reply:   [mds body][eadata] - ommited on error */
08609       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_mdt_body(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_mdt_body) ;
08610       if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST) {
08611         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_capa(tvb,offset,pinfo,tree, hf_lustre_capa, LUSTRE_REPLY_REC_OFF+1);
08612         offset=lustre_dissect_element_string(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_mds_xattr_name, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+2);
08613       }
08614       if (pb_type == PTL_RPC_MSG_REPLY)
08615         offset=lustre_dissect_element_data(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_mds_xattr_eadata, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+1);
08616       break;
08617     case MDS_GETATTR:
08618       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_mdt_body(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_mdt_body);
08619       if (pb_type == PTL_RPC_MSG_REPLY) { /*  [mdt_md][acl][capa1][capa2] */
08620         offset=lustre_dissect_element_string(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
08621                                              hf_lustre_mds_md_data,
08622                                              LUSTRE_REPLY_REC_OFF+1);
08623         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_acl(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
08624                                          hf_lustre_acl, LUSTRE_REPLY_REC_OFF+3);
08625         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_capa(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
08626                                           hf_lustre_capa,
08627                                           LUSTRE_REPLY_REC_OFF+4);
08628         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_capa(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
08629                                           hf_lustre_capa,
08630                                           LUSTRE_REPLY_REC_OFF+5);
08631       }
08632       break;
08633     case MDS_GETATTR_NAME:
08634       if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST)
08635         /*[mdt_body]*/
08636         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_mdt_body(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_mdt_body) ;
08637       /*[nothing in reply]*/
08638       break;
08639     case MDS_DONE_WRITING:
08640       /*[mdt_body]*/
08641       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_mdt_body(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_mdt_body) ;
08642       break;
08643     case MDS_PIN: /* repbody.. */
08644       /*[mdt_body]*/
08645       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_mdt_body(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_mdt_body) ;
08646       break;
08647     case MDS_SYNC:
08648       /*[mdt_body]*/
08649       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_mdt_body(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_mdt_body) ;
08650       break;
08651 
08652     case MDS_CLOSE:
08653       if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST)
08654       { /* [mdt_ioepoch][rec_reint][capa1] */
08655         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_mdt_ioepoch(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_mdt_ioepoch);
08656 
08657         if(LUSTRE_BUFFER_LEN(LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+1) > 0)
08658           offset=lustre_dissect_struct_mdt_rec_setattr(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_mdt_rec_setattr);
08659 
08660         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_capa(tvb,offset,pinfo,tree, hf_lustre_capa, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+2);
08661       }
08662       if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REPLY)
08663       { /* [mdt_body][md][cookie][capa1][capa2] */
08664         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_mdt_body(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_mdt_body) ;
08665         offset=lustre_dissect_element_string(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_mds_md_data, LUSTRE_REPLY_REC_OFF+1);
08666         if(LUSTRE_BUFFER_LEN(LUSTRE_REPLY_REC_OFF+2) > 0)
08667           offset=lustre_dissect_struct_llog_cookie(tvb,offset,pinfo,tree,hf_lustre_llog_cookie);
08668         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_capa(tvb,offset,pinfo,tree, hf_lustre_capa, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+3);
08669         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_capa(tvb,offset,pinfo,tree, hf_lustre_capa, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+4);
08670       }
08671       break;
08672 
08673     case MDS_STATFS:
08674       if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REPLY)
08675         /*[obd_statfs]*/
08676         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_obd_statfs(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_obd_statfs) ;
08677       /*in request : [nothing]*/
08678       break;
08679 
08680     case MDS_READPAGE:
08681       /* [mdt_body] but with some different interpration, need to modify the hf :  TODO  */
08682       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_mdt_body(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_mdt_body) ;
08683       break;
08684 
08685     case MDS_REINT:
08686       /* the structure depend on the intent_opcode */
08687       if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST)
08688         offset=reint_opcode_process(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
08689 
08690       if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REPLY) {
08691         /* [mdt_body][mdt_md][??][capa1][capa2] */
08692         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_mdt_body(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_mdt_body) ;
08693 
08694         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_lov_mds_md(tvb,offset,pinfo,tree,hf_lustre_lov_mds_md_v1, LUSTRE_REPLY_REC_OFF+1);
08695 
08696         if(LUSTRE_BUFFER_LEN(LUSTRE_REPLY_REC_OFF+2) > 0)
08697           /* open : ...[ACL]...
08698            * unlink, rename : ...[log_cookies]... */
08699           offset=lustre_dissect_element_data(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
08700                                              hf_lustre_mds_xattr_eadata,
08701                                              LUSTRE_REPLY_REC_OFF+2);
08702 
08703         lustre_dissect_struct_capa(tvb,offset,pinfo,tree, hf_lustre_capa, LUSTRE_REPLY_REC_OFF+3);
08704         lustre_dissect_struct_capa(tvb,offset,pinfo,tree, hf_lustre_capa, LUSTRE_REPLY_REC_OFF+4);
08705       }
08706       break;
08707     case MDS_SET_INFO:
08708       if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST){
08709         /*[key][val]*/
08710         offset=lustre_dissect_element_string(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ost_key,LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF); /* key  */
08711         offset=lustre_dissect_element_string(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ost_val, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+1); /* val */
08712         //offset=add_extra_padding(tvb,offset,pinfo,tree);
08713       }
08714       /*nothing en reply*/
08715       break;
08716     case MDS_QUOTACHECK:
08717       /* [obd_quotactl] */
08718       if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST)
08719         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_obd_quotactl(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_obd_quotactl) ;
08720       break;
08721     case MDS_QUOTACTL:
08722       /* [obd_quotactl] in both case*/
08723       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_obd_quotactl(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_obd_quotactl) ;
08724       break;
08725     case MDS_CONNECT:
08726       if (pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST) /* [targetuuid][clientuuid][lustre_handle][obd_connect_data] */
08727         offset=lustre_dissect_generic_connect(tvb,offset,pinfo,tree);
08728       if (pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REPLY || pb_type == PTL_RPC_MSG_ERR) /*[obd_connect_data]*/
08729         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_obd_connect_data(tvb,offset,pinfo,tree,hf_lustre_obd_connect_data);
08730       break;
08731     default:
08732       break;
08733   };
08734 
08735   return offset;
08736

08740 static int
08741 lustre_ldlm_opcode_process(tvbuff_t *tvb _U_, int offset _U_, packet_info *pinfo _U_, proto_tree * tree _U_, guint32 opc _U_, guint32 pb_type)
08742 {
08743   switch (opc) {
08744   case LDLM_ENQUEUE:
08745     /* [ldlm_request] if we have one more buffer it's
08746      * [intent_opcode] and the opcode give us the corresponding
08747      * intent structure [intent] */
08748     if (pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST) {
08749       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ldlm_request(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
08750                                                 hf_lustre_ldlm_request);
08751       if (LUSTRE_BUFCOUNT>=3)
08752         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ldlm_intent(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
08753                                                  hf_lustre_ldlm_intent);
08754     }
08755     if (pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REPLY) {
08756       guint32 ldlm_type;
08757       /*[ldlm_reply]*/
08758       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ldlm_reply(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
08759                                               hf_lustre_ldlm_reply,
08760                                               &ldlm_type);
08761       /* check if we're done processing */
08762       if (LUSTRE_BUFCOUNT <= 2)
08763           break;
08764 
08765       if (LUSTRE_BUFFER_LEN(LUSTRE_REPLY_REC_OFF) == 40)
08766         /* TODO :this code need to be check and test, the
08767          * lustre corresponding code isn't explicit, so not
08768          * sure to have this buffer, but in example it works
08769          * fine
08770          */
08771         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ost_lvb(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
08772                                              hf_lustre_ost_lvb);
08773 
08774       else if (ldlm_type == LDLM_EXTENT) {
08775         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_lov_mds_md(tvb,offset,pinfo,tree,hf_lustre_lov_mds_md_v1,
08776                                                 LUSTRE_DLM_REPLY_REC_OFF);
08777         break;
08778       }
08779 
08780       if (LUSTRE_BUFFER_LEN(LUSTRE_DLM_REPLY_REC_OFF) > 0)
08781         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_mdt_body(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
08782                                               hf_lustre_mdt_body);
08783       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_lov_mds_md(tvb,offset,pinfo,tree,hf_lustre_lov_mds_md_v1,
08784                                               LUSTRE_DLM_INTENT_REC_OFF);
08785 
08786       /* ldlm_intent_server : ACL */
08787       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_acl(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
08788                                        hf_lustre_acl, LUSTRE_DLM_INTENT_REC_OFF+1);
08789 
08790       /* ldlm_intent_open_server : [capa1][capa2] */
08791       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_capa(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
08792                                         hf_lustre_capa, LUSTRE_DLM_INTENT_REC_OFF+2);
08793       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_capa(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
08794                                         hf_lustre_capa, LUSTRE_DLM_INTENT_REC_OFF+3);
08795     }
08796     break;
08797 
08798   case LDLM_CONVERT:
08799     if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST) /*[ldlm_request]*/
08800       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ldlm_request(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ldlm_request) ;
08801     if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REPLY) /*[ldlm_reply]*/
08802       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ldlm_reply(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ldlm_reply, NULL) ;
08803     break;
08804 
08805   case LDLM_CANCEL:
08806     if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST) /*[ldlm_request]*/
08807       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ldlm_request(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ldlm_request) ;
08808     break;
08809 
08810   case LDLM_BL_CALLBACK:
08811     if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST) /*[ldlm_request]*/
08812       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ldlm_request(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ldlm_request) ;
08813     break;
08814 
08815   case LDLM_CP_CALLBACK:
08816     if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST){
08817       /*[ldlm_request] if the third buffer exist we have [lvb data] so it's [ost_lvb] : TODO :
08818        * check that */
08819       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ldlm_request(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ldlm_request) ;
08820       if(LUSTRE_BUFFER_LEN(LUSTRE_DLM_REPLY_REC_OFF) > 0)
08821         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ost_lvb(tvb,offset,pinfo,tree,hf_lustre_ost_lvb);
08822     }
08823     /*reply : [nothing] */
08824     break;
08825 
08826   case LDLM_GL_CALLBACK:
08827     if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST) { /*[ldlm_request] [lvb (for gl_desc)]*/
08828       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ldlm_request(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ldlm_request) ;
08829       if(LUSTRE_BUFFER_LEN(LUSTRE_DLM_REPLY_REC_OFF) > 0)
08830         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ost_lvb(tvb,offset,pinfo,tree,hf_lustre_ost_lvb);
08831     }
08832     if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REPLY) /* [ost_lvb] */
08833       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ost_lvb(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ost_lvb);
08834     break;
08835 
08836   default :
08837     break;
08838   }
08839   return offset;
08840 }

08913       break;

08916        * the size of second buf is LLOG_CHKUNK_SIZE, so it's maybee only bulk data */
08917       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_llogd_body(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_llogd_body);
08918       if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REPLY)
08919         offset=lustre_dissect_element_data(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_llogd_chunk,
08920                                            LUSTRE_REPLY_REC_OFF+1);
08921       break;
08922     case LLOG_ORIGIN_HANDLE_READ_HEADER:/* in handler.c */
08923       if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST){
08924         /* [llogd_body][llog_log_hdr] */
08925         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_llogd_body(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_llogd_body);
08926         if(LUSTRE_BUFCOUNT>2)
08927           offset=lustre_dissect_struct_llog_log_hdr(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
08928               hf_lustre_llogd_log_hdr);
08929       }
08930       if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REPLY) /* [llog_log_hdr] */
08931         offset=lustre_dissect_struct_llog_log_hdr(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
08932             hf_lustre_llogd_log_hdr);
08933       break;
08934     case LLOG_ORIGIN_HANDLE_WRITE_REC  : /* I think this is obsolete */
08935       /*[nothing]*/
08936       break;
08937     case LLOG_ORIGIN_HANDLE_CLOSE      :/* handler.c */
08938       /*[nothing]*/
08939       break;
08940     case LLOG_ORIGIN_CONNECT           : /* ost_handler.c */
08941       /*[nothing]*/
08942     case LLOG_CATINFO                  : /*in handler.c */
08943       if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REQUEST){
08944         /* [keyword][if keyword=config  [char*] else [nothing]] */
08945         offset=lustre_dissect_element_string(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_llogd_keyword,
08946                                              LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF);
08947         if (strcmp((const char *)tvb_get_string(tvb, LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF,
08948                                                 tvb_get_letohl(tvb,
08949                                                                LUSTRE_BUFLEN_OFF + 4 *
08950                                                                LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF)),
08951                    "config") == 0)
08952           /* if(keyword == "config") */
08953           offset=lustre_dissect_element_string(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_llogd_client,
08954                                                LUSTRE_REQ_REC_OFF+1);
08955       }
08956       if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REPLY)
08957         /*[buf] sizeof =  llog_chunk_size*/
08958         offset=lustre_dissect_element_data(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_llogd_chunk,
08959             LUSTRE_REPLY_REC_OFF + 1 );
08960       /* TODO TODO : check if it's note a catid */
08961       break;
08962     case LLOG_ORIGIN_HANDLE_PREV_BLOCK : /* in handler.c */
08963       /* [llogd_body] in both case */
08964       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_llogd_body(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_llogd_body);
08965       if(pb_type==PTL_RPC_MSG_REPLY)
08966         /*[buf] size of llog_chunk_size*/
08967         offset=lustre_dissect_element_data(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_llogd_chunk,
08968             LUSTRE_REPLY_REC_OFF + 1 );
08969       break;
08970     case LLOG_ORIGIN_HANDLE_DESTROY    : /* in handler.c */
08971       /*[llogd_body] in both case*/
08972       offset=lustre_dissect_struct_llogd_body(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_llogd_body);
08973       break;
08974     default:
08975       break;
08976   };
08977 
08978   return offset;
08979 }

09024 /* process lustre opcode :
09025    check if opcode is in range_opcode, and call the corresponding opcode process function */
09026 static int
09027 lustre_opcode_process(tvbuff_t *tvb _U_, int offset _U_, packet_info *pinfo _U_, proto_tree * tree _U_, guint32 opc _U_, guint32 pb_type)
09028 {
09029   /* No more buffers to process */
09030   if (LUSTRE_BUFCOUNT == 1)
09031     return offset;
09032 
09033   if (opc <= OST_LAST_OPC) /* OST opcodes */
09034     offset=lustre_ost_opcode_process( tvb , offset ,pinfo ,  tree , opc , pb_type) ;
09035 
09036   if ( (opc >= MDS_FIRST_OPC) &&  (opc < MDS_LAST_OPC )) /* MDS opcodes */
09037     offset=lustre_mds_opcode_process( tvb , offset ,pinfo ,  tree , opc , pb_type) ;
09038 
09039   if ( (opc >= LDLM_FIRST_OPC) && (opc < LDLM_LAST_OPC) ) /*LDLM Opcodes*/
09040     offset=lustre_ldlm_opcode_process( tvb , offset ,pinfo ,  tree , opc , pb_type) ;
09041 
09042   if( (opc>= MGS_FIRST_OPC) && (opc <= MGS_LAST_OPC)) /* MGS Opcodes */
09043     offset=lustre_mgs_opcode_process( tvb , offset ,pinfo ,  tree , opc , pb_type) ;
09044 
09045   if( (opc>= OBD_FIRST_OPC) && (opc<=OBD_LAST_OPC)) /* ODB Opcodes */
09046     offset=lustre_odb_opcode_process( tvb , offset ,pinfo ,  tree , opc , pb_type) ;
09047 
09048   if( (opc>=LLOG_FIRST_OPC) && (opc<=LLOG_LAST_OPC)) /* LLOG Opcodes */
09049     offset=lustre_llog_opcode_process( tvb , offset ,pinfo ,  tree , opc , pb_type) ;
09050 
09051   if( (opc >= SEQ_FIRST_OPC) && (opc <= SEQ_LAST_OPC) ) /* SEQ Opcodes */
09052     offset=lustre_seq_opcode_process(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, opc, pb_type);
09053 
09054   if( (opc >= FLD_FIRST_OPC) && (opc <= FLD_LAST_OPC) ) /* FLD Opcodes */
09055     offset=lustre_fld_opcode_process(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, opc, pb_type);
09056 
09057   return offset;
09058 }

09060 /* ----------------------------------------------- */
09061 /* add an extra padding to be aligned to 8bytes */
09062 static int
09063 add_extra_padding(tvbuff_t *tvb _U_, int offset _U_, packet_info *pinfo _U_, proto_tree * tree _U_)
09064 {
09065   guint32 padding_len;
09066 
09067   padding_len = (8- offset%8)%8;
09068   if(padding_len){
09069     proto_tree_add_item(tree, hf_lustre_extra_padding , tvb, offset, padding_len, TRUE);
09070     offset+=padding_len;
09071   }
09072   return offset;
09073 }

09076 static int
09077 ldlm_opcode_process(tvbuff_t *tvb _U_, int offset _U_, packet_info *pinfo _U_,
09078                     proto_tree * tree _U_, guint64 intent_opc _U_)
09079 {
09080   /* all corresponding code is in mdc_locks.c in function mdc_enqueue() */
09081   /* if 0x0003 we have CREAT + OPEN
09082    */
09083   if (intent_opc & IT_OPEN) {
09084     /* mdc_intent_open_pack(), d'o [opcode][mdc_rec_create][capa1][capa2][name][eada] */
09085     offset=lustre_dissect_struct_mdt_rec_create(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
09086                                                 hf_lustre_mdt_rec_create);
09087     offset=lustre_dissect_element_string(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
09088                                          hf_lustre_reint_name,
09089                                          LUSTRE_DLM_INTENT_REC_OFF+3);
09090     offset=lustre_dissect_element_data(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
09091                                        hf_lustre_mds_xattr_eadata,
09092                                        LUSTRE_DLM_INTENT_REC_OFF+4);
09093   }
09094 
09095   if (intent_opc & IT_UNLINK){
09096     /* mdc_intent_unlink_pack(), d'o [opcode][mdt_rec_unlink][capa][name] */
09097     offset=lustre_dissect_struct_mdt_rec_unlink(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
09098                                                 hf_lustre_mdt_rec_unlink);
09099     offset=lustre_dissect_struct_capa(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_capa,
09100                                       LUSTRE_DLM_INTENT_REC_OFF+1);
09101     offset=lustre_dissect_element_string(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree,
09102                                          hf_lustre_reint_name,
09103                                          LUSTRE_DLM_INTENT_REC_OFF+2);
09104   }
09105   if (intent_opc & IT_GETATTR){
09106     /* mdc_intent_lookup_pack, d'o [mdt_body][capa][name] */
09107     offset=lustre_dissect_struct_mdt_body(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_mdt_body) ;
09108     offset=lustre_dissect_struct_capa(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_capa,
09109                                       LUSTRE_DLM_INTENT_REC_OFF+1);
09110     offset=lustre_dissect_element_string(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_reint_name,
09111                                          LUSTRE_DLM_INTENT_REC_OFF+2);
09112   }
09113 
09114   if (intent_opc & IT_LOOKUP){
09115     /* mdc_intent_lookup_pack, d'o [mdt_body][capa][name] */
09116     offset=lustre_dissect_struct_mdt_body(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_mdt_body);
09117     offset=lustre_dissect_struct_capa(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_capa,
09118                                       LUSTRE_DLM_INTENT_REC_OFF+1);
09119     offset=lustre_dissect_element_string(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_reint_name,
09120                                          LUSTRE_DLM_INTENT_REC_OFF+2);
09121   }
09122   return offset;
09123 }

09128 /* function to test if the packet is entirely dissected  add BUG in PROTOCOL COL when it's not*/
09129 static void
09130 sanity_check(tvbuff_t *tvb, packet_info *pinfo, guint32 val_offset _U_)
09131 {
09132   guint32 somme_buflen = 0 ;
09133   guint32 i ;
09134 
09135   /* magic_number = tvb_get_letohl(tvb, 8); */
09136 
09137   for (i=0;i<LUSTRE_BUFCOUNT;i++)
09138     somme_buflen += tvb_get_letohl(tvb, LUSTRE_BUFLEN_OFF +
09139         4 * i ) + (8- tvb_get_letohl(tvb, LUSTRE_BUFLEN_OFF+4 * i)%8)%8; /* we add the
09140                                                                             corresponding
09141                                                                             extra padding,
09142                                                                             because extra
09143                                                                             padding isn't
09144                                                                             count in buflen
09145                                                                             */
09146 
09147   if(val_offset!=somme_buflen){
09148     /*g_print("somme_buflen=%d, val_offset = %d \n",somme_buflen,val_offset);*/
09149     if (check_col(pinfo->cinfo, COL_INFO)) {
09150       col_append_str(pinfo->cinfo, COL_PROTOCOL, "BUG");
09151     }
09152   }
09153 
09154 }

09539 static int
09540 lustre_dissect_struct_ptlrpc_body(tvbuff_t *tvb _U_, int offset _U_, packet_info *pinfo _U_, proto_tree *parent_tree _U_, int hf_index _U_, guint32 buf_len _U_ )
09541 {
09542   proto_item *item = NULL;
09543   proto_tree *tree = NULL;
09544   int old_offset, i;
09545   guint32 opc, pb_type, pb_version;
09546 
09547   old_offset=offset;
09548 
09549   if (parent_tree) {
09550     item = proto_tree_add_item(parent_tree, hf_index, tvb, offset, -1, TRUE);
09551     tree = proto_item_add_subtree(item, ett_lustre_ptlrpc_body);
09552   }
09553 
09554   offset=lustre_dissect_element_ptlrpc_body_pb_handle(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09555 
09556   pb_type = tvb_get_letohl(tvb, offset);
09557   //g_print("msg_v2_lm_type_offset = %d \n" , offset) ;
09558 
09559   offset=lustre_dissect_element_ptlrpc_body_pb_type(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09560 
09561   pb_version = tvb_get_letohl(tvb, offset) & ~LUSTRE_VERSION_MASK;
09562   //g_print("msg_v2_version_offset %d : version == %d \n", offset, pb_version);
09563   offset=lustre_dissect_element_ptlrpc_body_pb_version(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09564 
09565   // g_print("msg_v2_opcode_offset %d  \n", offset);
09566   opc = tvb_get_letohl(tvb, offset);
09567   offset=lustre_dissect_element_ptlrpc_body_pb_opc(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09568 
09569   offset=lustre_dissect_element_ptlrpc_body_pb_status(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09570 
09571   offset=lustre_dissect_element_ptlrpc_body_pb_last_xid(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09572 
09573   offset=lustre_dissect_element_ptlrpc_body_pb_last_seen(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09574 
09575   offset=lustre_dissect_element_ptlrpc_body_pb_last_committed(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09576 
09577   offset=lustre_dissect_element_ptlrpc_body_pb_transno(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09578 
09579   offset=lustre_dissect_element_ptlrpc_body_pb_flags(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09580 
09581   offset=lustre_dissect_element_ptlrpc_body_pb_op_flags(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09582 
09583   offset=lustre_dissect_element_ptlrpc_body_pb_conn_cnt(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09584 
09585   offset=lustre_dissect_element_ptlrpc_body_pb_timeout(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09586 
09587   offset=lustre_dissect_element_ptlrpc_body_pb_service_time(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09588 
09589   offset=lustre_dissect_element_ptlrpc_body_pb_limit(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09590 
09591   offset=lustre_dissect_element_ptlrpc_body_pb_slv(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09592 
09593   /* pb_pre_versions */
09594   for(i = 0; i < 4; ++i) {
09595     offset=lustre_dissect_element_ptlrpc_body_pb_pre_version(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09596   }
09597 
09598   for(i = 0; i < 4; ++i) {
09599     offset=lustre_dissect_element_ptlrpc_body_pb_padding(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09600   }
09601 
09602   if (pb_version == LUSTRE_PTLRPC_MSG_VERSION && offset-old_offset < buf_len) {
09603     offset=lustre_dissect_element_ptlrpc_body_pb_jobid(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09604   }
09605 
09606   if (offset-old_offset != buf_len) {
09607     g_print("ptlbody offset-old:%d buf_len:%d\n",
09608             offset-old_offset, buf_len);
09609     col_append_str(pinfo->cinfo, COL_PROTOCOL, "BUG");
09610   }
09611 
09612   proto_item_set_len(item, offset-old_offset);
09613 
09614   /* display some nice infos */
09615   display_info_str(parent_tree, pinfo->cinfo, COL_INFO, val_to_str(opc, lustre_op_codes, "Unknown"));
09616   display_info_fstr(parent_tree, pinfo->cinfo,COL_INFO, " %s ", val_to_str(pb_type, lustre_LMTypes, "Unknown"));
09617 
09618   /* on utilise parent_tree pour bien distinguer les diffrents buffers (relatifs  bufcount + buflen), il s'agit d'un choix de prsentation */
09619   offset=lustre_opcode_process(tvb, offset, pinfo, parent_tree, opc, pb_type);
09620 
09621   sanity_check(tvb,pinfo,offset-old_offset);
09622   return offset;
09623 }

09713 int
09714 lustre_dissect_struct_msg_v2(tvbuff_t *tvb _U_, int offset _U_, packet_info *pinfo _U_, proto_tree *parent_tree _U_, int hf_index _U_)
09715 {
09716   proto_item *item = NULL;
09717   proto_tree *tree = NULL;
09718   guint32 bufcount ;
09719   int old_offset;
09720   guint32 i ;
09721   guint32 buf_len_offset;
09722   guint32 current_buf_len ;
09723   gboolean extra_padding ;
09724 
09725 
09726   old_offset=offset;
09727   /* to get a light display */
09728   tree=parent_tree;
09729   //  if (parent_tree) {
09730   //      item = proto_tree_add_item(parent_tree, hf_index, tvb, offset, -1, TRUE);
09731   //      tree = proto_item_add_subtree(item, ett_lustre_lustre_msg_v2);
09732   //  }
09733 
09734   bufcount = tvb_get_letohl(tvb,offset);
09735   offset=lustre_dissect_element_msg_v2_lm_bufcount(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09736 
09737   offset=lustre_dissect_element_msg_v2_lm_secflvr(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09738 
09739   offset=lustre_dissect_element_msg_v2_lm_magic(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09740 
09741   offset=lustre_dissect_element_msg_v2_lm_repsize(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09742 
09743   offset=lustre_dissect_element_msg_v2_lm_cksum(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09744 
09745   offset=lustre_dissect_element_msg_v2_lm_flags(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09746 
09747   offset=lustre_dissect_element_msg_v2_lm_padding_2(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09748 
09749   offset=lustre_dissect_element_msg_v2_lm_padding_3(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09750 
09751 
09752 
09753   if (bufcount & 1) /* we add an extra padding if bufcount is odd */
09754     extra_padding = 1 ;
09755   else
09756     extra_padding = 0 ;
09757 
09758   buf_len_offset=offset ;
09759   for (i=0;i<bufcount;i++) {
09760     offset=lustre_dissect_element_msg_v2_lm_buflens_(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree);
09761   }
09762 
09763   if (extra_padding)
09764   {
09765     offset=dissect_uint32(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_extra_padding);
09766   }
09767 
09768   current_buf_len = tvb_get_letohl(tvb, buf_len_offset);
09769   offset=lustre_dissect_struct_ptlrpc_body(tvb,offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ptlrpc_body_pb, current_buf_len);
09770 
09771   proto_item_set_len(item, offset-old_offset);
09772 
09773   return offset;
09774 }
